# Project Standards
- Tech Stack: Next.js 15+ (App Router), Tailwind CSS, Framer Motion, Lucide React.
- Language: Bilingual (English & Serbian) using next-intl or similar i18n library.
- Styling: Modern, minimalist, high-end furniture brand aesthetic.
- Components: Functional components with TypeScript. Use clean, modular architecture.
- Animations: Smooth, scroll-triggered, luxury feel.